title: [Fujishima Kosuke] Ah! My Goddess (001-308 and extras)
description:
This archive contains all 308 chapters of the manga series, Ah! My Goddess by Fujishima Kosuke. It ran in the magazine Afternoon from 1988 to 2014. It was licensed and released in English as Oh! My Goddess by Dark Horse Comics.

This archive combines chapters released by the following sources:

Chapters 1 - 34: Scanlations by Goddess Miyaku Team
Chapters 35 - 85: Dark Horse Comics "flipped" editions, 35 to 78 scanned by "headcrab", 79 to 85 by an unknown source.
Chapters 86 - 176: Scanlations by the group lead by HemisH
Chapters 177 - 308: Scanlations by Goddess Miyaku Team

Adventures of the Mini-Goddesses: Dark Horse Comics "flipped" edition scanned by "headcrab" (previously named "omg-special" by "headcrab")

Ah! My Goddess Colours: Scanlations by Goddess Miyaku Team, plus scans of the last sections of the Dark Horse Comics English release.

Scans of the manga volume covers and supplemental pages have been taken from online scans of the Japanese manga volumes and placed with the appropriate chapters where previously absent.

For more details, please read the included release notes
